name: Tales of Time by Jabi Sanz V2

metadata.name: Arctic Sea
metadata.description:
Fire leaving battle scars after a heated war.

Air dancing across the desert and sweeping the sand with her skirt.

Water being frozen in time by the bite of winter and being kissed alive by the rays of the sun.

Earth submitting to the powerful forces of her three sister elements.

These are the stories written by the four pillars of nature. Characters who act out each scene and leave an ever changing landscape in their wake.

Tales of Time is a collection of these stories. Each image is a unique fingerprint of a moment in time, captured brilliantly by Jabi Sanz
